com.facebook.buck.skylark.parser

Class LoadImport

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.skylark.parser.LoadImport

  • @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
 @Generated(value="org.immutables.processor.ProxyProcessor")
 @Immutable
 @CheckReturnValue
public final class LoadImport
extends Object
    A value object for information about load function import, since SkylarkImport does not provide enough context. For instance, the same SkylarkImport can represent different logical imports depending on which repository it is resolved in.
